# ===== OAuth (Google) =====
# Configure OAuth providers in Supabase Dashboard:
# 1. Go to: Supabase Dashboard → Authentication → Providers → Google
# 2. Enable Google provider
# 3. Get Client ID and Client Secret from: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# 4. Configure Authorized redirect URI:
#    Local: http://localhost:3000/auth/callback
#    Supabase: https://[PROJECT_REF].supabase.co/auth/v1/callback
#    Production: https://symplepass.com/auth/callback
#
# Note: OAuth credentials are configured in Supabase Dashboard, not as environment variables
# The /auth/callback route handler processes the OAuth callback automatically

